 <span data-ttu-id="26aa6-102">将 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext> 的实现传递给 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> 和 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyImportExtension> 对象，可以分别从元数据导出自定义策略断言，或将自定义策略断言导入元数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26aa6-102">An implementation of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext> is passed to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyImportExtension> objects to export and import, respectively, custom policy assertions to and from metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="26aa6-103">导出时，会检索策略断言集合，以便添加自定义断言。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26aa6-103">On export, a collection of policy assertions are retrieved in order to add custom assertions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="26aa6-104">导入时，会检索断言，以便导入特定断言并相应地对绑定元素进行配置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26aa6-104">On import, the assertions are retrieved in order to import specific ones and configure binding elements appropriately.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="26aa6-105"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext.GetBindingAssertions%2A> 方法可返回绑定的所有策略断言。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26aa6-105">The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext.GetBindingAssertions%2A> method returns all policy assertions that are for the binding.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="26aa6-106"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext.GetFaultBindingAssertions%2A> 方法可返回特定错误消息的所有策略断言。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26aa6-106">The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext.GetFaultBindingAssertions%2A> method returns all policy assertions for a specific fault message.</span></span>  
  
